node.text: I am saddened by the news I just received about my brother Vincent Jackson. Off-season training we pushed each other to become better players. So grateful to have teamed up with you in for a year in Tampa Bay. My sincerest condolences goes to the family. We will miss you. Rest in Paradise! ❤️
